h4. Actor:
Administrator, Remittance User, Exchange House User

h4. Description:
This is the landing page for *Approve Task* Search Panel on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow: 
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Disbursement sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Approve" link from left menu under task .
* Show landing page for "Approve Task".

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show for approve Task" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get empty list in grid view.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show blank list in grid view.
** Blank search form on top to search for "Approve Task".

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

